title: #92Noon! Fair/Fleck/Gleeman/Guerin Presser
description: It's the first day of the Minnesota State fair and PA is kicking it off. Head coach of the Minnesota Gophers joins the fun, Twins scholar, Aaron Gleeman, stick through the entire program, and we have the press conference introducing the new GM to the Wild, Bill Guerin.
